      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against FDA benchmark CFD challenge results (Stewart et al. 2012). Lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step benchmarks confirm correct Navier-Stokes discretization. Power-law hemolysis transport equation implementation verified against analytical solution for simple shear flow."
    },
    {
