      "rationale": "Three-level grid refinement study performed: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (5.8M cells), fine (14.2M cells). Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 2.3% for NIH at worst-case operating point. Observed order of convergence 1.87, consistent with second-order spatial discretization. Fine mesh adopted for all production runs."
    },
